在上面的代码中，我们重写了 `append` 方法并添加了代码过滤，只记录执行的SQL语句。

2. 设置Spring Boot日志

在Spring Boot配置文件（如 `application.yml`）中，将日志级别设置为 `DEBUG`，并设置 `org.hibernate.SQL` 和 `org.hibernate.type` 的日志级别为 `DEBUG` 或 `TRACE`。

```yaml
logging:
  level:
    root: DEBUG
    org.hibernate.SQL: DEBUG
    org.hibernate.type.descriptor.sql.BasicBinder: TRACE
  appenders:
    console:
      name: console
      threshold: DEBUG
      target: SYSTEM_OUT
      encoder:
        pattern: "%d{yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss.SSS} [%thread] %-5level %logger{36} - %msg%n"
        charset: UTF-8
  loggers:
    com.example:
      level: DEBUG
      additivity: false
      appenders: console
```

在上面的配置中，我们将日志级别设置为 `DEBUG`，并设置 `org.hibernate.SQL` 和 `org.hibernate.type` 的日志级别为 `DEBUG` 或 `TRACE`。这将启用Hibernate的SQL语句日志记录功能。

3. 设置SessionFactory属性

我们需要为 `SessionFactory` 设置属性，以便在Hibernate中启用SQL语句日志记录。在Spring Boot配置类中，我们可以添加以下代码：

```java
@Bean
public LocalSessionFactoryBean sessionFactory() {
    LocalSessionFactoryBean sessionFactoryBean = new LocalSessionFactoryBean();
    sessionFactoryBean.setDataSource(dataSource());
    sessionFactoryBean.setPackagesToScan("com.example.demo");
    Properties hibernateProperties = new Properties();
    hibernateProperties.put("hibernate.show_sql", "false");
    hibernateProperties.put("hibernate.format_sql", "false");
    hibernateProperties.put("hibernate.use_sql_comments", "false");
    hibernateProperties.put("hibernate.generate_statistics", "false");
    hibernateProperties.put("hibernate.type", "trace");
    hibernateProperties.put("hibernate.session.events.log", "true");
    hibernateProperties.put("hibernate.session.events.log.flush_entity", "true");
    sessionFactoryBean.setHibernateProperties(hibernateProperties);
    return sessionFactoryBean;
}
```

在上面的代码中，我们将 `hibernate.show_sql`、`hibernate.format_sql` 和 `hibernate.use_sql_comments` 属性设置为 `false`，以隐藏Hibernate的SQL语句日志记录。然而，我们将 `hibernate.type` 属性设置为 `trace`，以启用SQL参数的跟踪性能。还将 `hibernate.session.events.log` 和 `hibernate.session.events.log.flush_entity` 属性设置为 `true`，以便记录Entity被保存时的SQL语句。

完成这些步骤后，你可以执行一些查询并观察日志来验证切面操作是否使用正确。所有执行的SQL语句将被记录在日志中。

在Spring Boot中使用JPA，我们可以使用Hibernate作为JPA的提供者。要获取JPA执行成功的SQL语句，我们可以通过以下方法：

1. 在application.properties文件中将以下配置项设置为true：

spring.jpa.show-sql=true

这将启用Hibernate的SQL日志功能，每次执行JPA操作时，Hibernate都会将生成的SQL语句打印出来。

2. 可以将日志级别设置为DEBUG，以便查看更详细的日志信息。在application.properties文件中添加以下行：

logging.level.org.hibernate.SQL=DEBUG

这将启用Hibernate的SQL日志记录器，并记录SQL语句和参数值。

3. 如果希望在代码中获取JPA执行的SQL语句，可以通过以下方式进行：

@Repository
public class SomeRepository {

  @PersistenceContext
  private EntityManager entityManager;

  public void someMethod() {
    String sql = entityManager.createQuery("SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SomeEntity").unwrap(org.hibernate.query.Query.class).getQueryString();
    System.out.println(sql);
  }
}

这将打印出“SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SomeEntity”SQL语句的字符串表示形式。注意，需要使用unwrap方法将JPA查询对象转换为Hibernate查询对象，才能获取SQL语句。

以上就是获取JPA执行成功的SQL语句的方法，可以根据需要选择适合自己的方式。

在Spring Boot中使用AOP拦截JPA执行操作的过程，可以在方法执行前后获取执行成功的SQL语句。

1. 创建一个AOP切面类来拦截JPA执行操作的方法，可以在该类中使用@Before或@After注解来拦截方法执行前或执行后的时机。例如：

@Aspect
@Component
public class JpaSqlAspect {

  @Before("execution(* com.example.repository.*.*(..))")
  public void before(JoinPoint joinPoint) {
    // 拦截JPA执行操作前的逻辑
    System.out.println("JPA执行操作前： " + joinPoint.getSignature().getName());
  }

  @AfterReturning(value = "execution(* com.example.repository.*.*(..))", returning = "result")
  public void afterReturning(JoinPoint joinPoint, Object result) {
    // 拦截JPA执行操作后的逻辑
    System.out.println("JPA执行操作后： " + joinPoint.getSignature().getName());
    if (result instanceof List<?>) {
      List<?> entities = (List<?>) result;
      for (Object entity : entities) {
        String sql = ((SessionImplementor) entityManager.getDelegate()).getEntityPersister(null, entity)
            .getSQLInsertStrings((Session) entityManager.getDelegate(), entity)[0];
        System.out.println(sql);
      }
    } else {
      String sql = ((SessionImplementor) entityManager.getDelegate()).getTransactionCoordinator().getJdbcCoordinator()
          .getResultSetReturn().extractSqlString((CallableStatement) result);
      System.out.println(sql);
    }
  }

  @Autowired
  private EntityManager entityManager;

}

以上切面类中@Before注解拦截了所有com.example.repository包下的方法执行前的操作，@AfterReturning注解拦截了所有com.example.repository包下的方法执行后的操作，并执行了获取SQL的逻辑。

2. JPA的操作需要注入EntityManager对象，可以使用@Autowired注解将entityManager注入到切面类中。

3. 在@AfterReturning注解中，可以通过判断返回结果的类型来判断执行的是查询操作还是更新操作。如果是查询操作，可以将返回的实体对象遍历并获取其对应的SQL语句；如果是更新操作，可以通过result对象来获取SQL语句。

通过以上方式，就可以在AOP切面中获取JPA执行成功的SQL语句了。注意，此方法要求Hibernate版本不低于5.4。

在Spring Boot中，JPA使用EntityManager对象进行数据库操作。我们可以通过EntityManager对象获取JPA执行成功的SQL语句。

1. 查询操作的获取方式

在查询操作中，我们可以使用JPA的createQuery方法来创建查询，然后通过getJpaQuery方法获取JPA执行的查询操作语句，例如：

```
Query query = entityManager.createQuery("SELECT p FROM Person p WHERE p.age >= :age");
query.setParameter("age", 18);
String nativeSql = ((org.hibernate.query.Query)query).getHibernateQuery().getQueryString();
System.out.println(nativeSql);
```

2. 更新操作的获取方式

在更新操作中，我们可以使用JPA的createNativeQuery或者createNamedQuery方法来创建原生SQL或命名查询，然后通过unwrap方法获取Hibernate的底层操作对象并获取执行的SQL语句，例如：

```
String sql = "UPDATE Person SET age = :age WHERE id = :id";
Query query = entityManager.createNativeQuery(sql);
query.setParameter("age", 18);
query.setParameter("id", 1L);
String nativeSql = query.unwrap(org.hibernate.query.NativeQuery.class).getQueryString();
System.out.println(nativeSql);
```

```
Query query = entityManager.createNamedQuery("Person.updateAgeById");
query.setParameter("age", 18);
query.setParameter("id", 1L);
String nativeSql = query.unwrap(org.hibernate.query.NativeQuery.class).getQueryString();
System.out.println(nativeSql);
```

通过以上方法，我们就可以获取JPA执行成功的SQL语句了。

在Spring Boot中使用Oracle的UCP连接池，可以结合Log4jdbc-Remix来记录JDBC SQL执行日志。

以下是使用Log4jdbc-Remix记录JDBC执行日志的步骤：

1. 在Maven中添加依赖

在pom.xml文件中添加以下依赖：

```
<dependency>
  <groupId>com.oracle.database.jdbc</groupId>
  <artifactId>Ucp</artifactId>
  <version>19.3.0.0</version>
</dependency>

<dependency>
  <groupId>org.bgee.log4jdbc-remix</groupId>
  <artifactId>log4jdbc-remix</artifactId>
  <version>0.2.7</version>
</dependency>

<dependency>
  <groupId>commons-logging</groupId>
  <artifactId>commons-logging</artifactId>
  <version>1.2</version>
</dependency>
```

2. 配置连接池

在application.yml文件中添加以下配置：

```
oracle:
 datasource:
   url: jdbc:oracle:thin:@localhost:1521:ORCL
   user: scott
   password: tiger
   driver-class-name: oracle.jdbc.driver.OracleDriver
   pool:
     minPoolSize: 5
     maxPoolSize: 20
```

在@Configuration类中配置DataSource

```
@Configuration
@ConfigurationProperties(prefix = "oracle.datasource")
public class DataSourceConfig {

  private String url;
  private String user;
  private String password;
  private String driverClassName;

  private PoolConfig pool = new PoolConfig();

  @Bean
  public DataSource dataSource() throws SQLException {

    Properties properties = new Properties();
    properties.setProperty("v$session.osuser", System.getProperty("user.name"));

    OracleDataSource dataSource = new OracleDataSource();
    dataSource.setURL(url);
    dataSource.setUser(user);
    dataSource.setPassword(password);
    dataSource.setConnectionProperties(properties);

    UCPDataSource ucpDataSource = new UCPDataSource();
    ucpDataSource.setConnectionFactoryClassName(dataSource.getClass().getName());
    ucpDataSource.setURL(dataSource.getURL());
    ucpDataSource.setUser(dataSource.getUser());
    ucpDataSource.setPassword(dataSource.getPassword());

    PoolDataSource poolDataSource = PoolDataSourceFactory.getPoolDataSource();
    poolDataSource.createConnectionBuilder()
        .url(ucpDataSource.getUrl())
        .username(ucpDataSource.getUser())
        .password(ucpDataSource.getPassword())
        .connectionFactoryClassName(ucpDataSource.getConnectionFactoryClassName())
        .connectionProperties(properties)
        .validateConnectionOnBorrow(true)
        .build();

    poolDataSource.setConnectionFactory(ucpDataSource);
    poolDataSource.setConnectionPoolName("UCP_example_pool");
    poolDataSource.setInitialPoolSize(pool.getMinPoolSize());
    poolDataSource.setMaxPoolSize(pool.getMaxPoolSize());

    return new DataSourceSpy(poolDataSource);
  }

  public static class PoolConfig {
    private int minPoolSize;
    private int maxPoolSize;

    // getters and setters
  }

  // getters and setters
}
```

3. 在logback.xml文件中配置Log4jdbc-Remix

在logback.xml文件中添加以下配置：

```
<logger name="jdbc.audit" level="OFF" />
<logger name="jdbc.connection" level="OFF" />
<logger name="jdbc.resultset" level="OFF" />
<logger name="jdbc.sqltiming" level="DEBUG" />

<appender name="STDOUT" class="ch.qos.logback.core.ConsoleAppender">
  <encoder>
    <pattern>%date [%thread] %-5level %logger{36} - %message%n</pattern>
  </encoder>
</appender>

<appender name="JDBC_LOGGING" class="net.sf.log4jdbc.log.slf4j.Slf4jSpyLogDelegator">
  <param name="connectionLoggingEnabled" value="false" />
  <param name="connectionIdLoggingEnabled" value="false" />
  <param name="resultsetCloseLoggingEnabled" value="false" />
  <param name="debugLevel" value="INFO" />
</appender>

<root level="INFO">
  <appender-ref ref="STDOUT"/>
  <appender-ref ref="JDBC_LOGGING"/>
</root>
```

这将启用Log4jdbc-Remix的SpyLogDelegator，并将JDBC执行日志写入到日志中。

通过以上步骤，JDBC执行日志将被记录到日志中。

对于SpringBoot AOP的成功事务执行的SQL，我们需要在代码中使用@Transactional注释来标记一个事务方法，然后使用SpringBoot AOP的@AfterReturning注释来捕获成功执行的SQL。下面是一个示例代码：

```
@Service
public class UserService {
    @Autowired
    private JdbcTemplate jdbcTemplate;

    @Transactional
    public User createUser(String name, int age) {
        // insert user into database
        String sql = "INSERT INTO user(name, age) VALUES (?, ?)";
        int result = jdbcTemplate.update(sql, name, age);

        // return created user
        User user = new User();
        user.setName(name);
        user.setAge(age);
        return user;
    }
}

@Aspect
@Component
public class TransactionAspect {
    @Autowired
    private JdbcTemplate jdbcTemplate;

    @AfterReturning(pointcut = "execution(* com.example.UserService.*(..))")
    public void afterReturningAdvice(JoinPoint joinPoint) {
        // if method is transactional
        if (joinPoint.getSignature().getName().contains("Transaction")) {
            // get SQL statement
            String sql = jdbcTemplate.getDataSource().getConnection().prepareStatement("SELECT LAST_INSERT_ID()").executeQuery().getString(1);
            System.out.println("SQL executed successfully: " + sql);
        }
    }
}
```

在上面的代码示例中，我们首先定义了一个UserService类，其中有一个使用@Transactional注释进行标记的createUser()方法。在TransactionAspect类中，我们使用Spring AOP的@AfterReturning注释捕获了成功执行的SQL语句。我们还使用了JdbcTemplate来获取数据源并查询最后插入的ID以获得成功执行的SQL语句。最后，我们使用System.out.println()方法打印成功执行的SQL语句。

对于SpringBoot AOP捕获成功事务执行的SQL queryDSL，我们需要使用QueryDSL库来构建SQL查询链，然后使用SpringBoot AOP的@AfterReturning注释来捕获成功执行的SQL。下面是一个示例代码：

```
@Service
public class UserService {
    @Autowired
    private JPAQueryFactory queryFactory;

    @Transactional
    public User createUser(String name, int age) {
        // insert user into database
        QUser qUser = QUser.user;
        queryFactory.insert(qUser).set(qUser.name, name).set(qUser.age, age).execute();

        // return created user
        User user = new User();
        user.setName(name);
        user.setAge(age);
        return user;
    }
}

@Aspect
@Component
public class TransactionAspect {
    @Autowired
    private JPAQueryFactory queryFactory;

    @AfterReturning(pointcut = "execution(* com.example.UserService.*(..))")
    public void afterReturningAdvice(JoinPoint joinPoint) {
        // if method is transactional
        if (joinPoint.getSignature().getName().contains("Transaction")) {
            // get SQL statement
            String sql = queryFactory.select(SQLExpressions.stringTemplate("QUERYDSL_DEBUG")).fetchFirst();
            System.out.println("SQL executed successfully: " + sql);
        }
    }
}
```

在上面的代码示例中，我们首先定义了一个UserService类，其中有一个使用@Transactional注释进行标记的createUser()方法。在TransactionAspect类中，我们使用Spring AOP的@AfterReturning注释捕获了成功执行的SQL语句。我们使用QueryDSL库构建了SQL查询链，并使用SQLExpressions.stringTemplate()方法创建了一个查询，返回一个字符串“QUERYDSL_DEBUG”，从而获得成功执行的SQL语句。最后，我们使用System.out.println()方法打印成功执行的SQL语句。

对于SpringBoot AOP获取QueryDSL执行SQL，我们可以通过在QueryDslJpaRepository或QueryDslRepositorySupport bean中配置一个自定义的QuerydslBinderCustomizer来添加SQLListener，并在SQLListener实现中获取SQL信息。下面是一个示例代码：

首先，定义一个SQLListener类来捕获SQL信息：

```
public class SQLListener {

    @PrePersist
    @PreUpdate
    @PreRemove
    public void onPrePersist(Object entity) {
        String sql = SQLTemplates.DEFAULT.toQueryString(new SQLSerializer(SQLTemplates.DEFAULT).serialize(entity));
        System.out.println("SQL executed successfully: " + sql);
    }

}
```

接下来，在自定义的QuerydslBinderCustomizer中添加SQLListener到查询对象的监听器列表中：

```
public class CustomQuerydslBinderCustomizer implements QuerydslBinderCustomizer<QUser> {

    @Override
    public void customize(QuerydslBindings bindings, QUser user) {
        JPAQueryFactory queryFactory = new JPAQueryFactory(entityManager);
        SQLListener sqlListener = new SQLListener();
        queryFactory.register(sqlListener);

        bindings.setValidator(new SpringValidatorAdapter(validator));
        bindings.bind(User.class).first((SingleValueBinding<User>) (path, value) -> path.eq(value));
    }

}
```

最后，在@Repository中注入CustomQuerydslBinderCustomizer：

```
@Repository
public interface UserRepository extends QueryDslJpaRepository<User, Long>, UserRepositoryCustom, QuerydslPredicateExecutor<User> {

    CustomQuerydslBinderCustomizer customizer = new CustomQuerydslBinderCustomizer();

}
```

这样，当我们调用UserRepository的方法执行查询操作时，SQLListener就会被调用，并且我们可以在SQLListener的实现中获取SQL信息。

对于SpringBoot AOP捕获Hibernate执行的成功事务SQL，我们需要在代码中使用@Transactional注释来标记一个事务方法，然后使用Hibernate的Interceptor注册一个回调。下面是一个示例代码：

首先，定义一个实现Hibernate的Interceptor接口的类，在onPrepareStatement方法中可以获取到SQL信息：

```
@Component
public class HibernateInterceptor implements Interceptor {
    @Override
    public String onPrepareStatement(String sql) {
        System.out.println("SQL executed successfully: " + sql);
        return sql;
    }

    // 其他方法省略
}
```

接下来，在应用程序的配置文件中注册HibernateInterceptor作为Hibernate的Interceptors：

```
spring.jpa.properties.hibernate.session_factory.interceptor=com.example.HibernateInterceptor
```

最后，在标记为@Transactional注释的事务方法内执行Hibernate代码：

```
@Service
public class UserService {
    @Autowired
    private SessionFactory sessionFactory;

    @Transactional
    public User createUser(String name, int age) {
        // insert user into database
        Session session = sessionFactory.getCurrentSession();
        String hql = "insert into User(name, age) values(:name, :age)";
        Query query = session.createQuery(hql);
        query.setParameter("name", name);
        query.setParameter("age", age);
        query.executeUpdate();

        // return created user
        User user = new User();
        user.setName(name);
        user.setAge(age);
        return user;
    }
}
```

当我们调用UserService的createUser()方法时，HibernateInterceptor就会被调用，在HibernateInterceptor的实现中，我们可以获取到该SQL执行的信息。

可以通过在SpringBoot应用程序中启用日志记录可以获取成功事务的SQL。

第一种方法是使用application.properties文件配置日志级别。

1.在application.properties文件中，添加以下配置：

logging.level.org.springframework.transaction=TRACE

2.保存文件并重新启动应用程序。在应用程序的日志输出中，你应该可以看到所有的事务操作SQL。

第二种方法是在Java代码中配置日志级别。

1.在应用程序的Java类中，添加以下代码：

Logger logger = LoggerFactory.getLogger(getClass());
CustomLogMessage logMessage = new CustomLogMessage();

2.在执行成功事务操作的方法中添加日志记录：

@Transactional(propagation = Propagation.REQUIRED)
public void doSomething() {
  //perform successful transaction operations
  logger.trace("{}", logMessage.transactionSuccess("doSomething"));
}

3.创建一个"CustomLogMessage"类，在该类中定义一个"transactionSuccess"方法，该方法将事务操作名称作为参数，并返回一个字符串：

public class CustomLogMessage {
  public String transactionSuccess(String transactionName) {
    return "Successful transaction for " + transactionName;
  }
}

4.启动应用程序并运行成功的事务操作。在应用程序的日志输出中，你应该能够看到你的成功事务操作的SQL。

Spring Boot允许我们使用AOP来记录成功事务的SQL。跟前一题所述的日志记录方式不同，AOP会自动记录所有的事务操作SQL，而不需要在每个事务操作中添加特定的日志。

以下是如何使用AOP获取成功事务的SQL：

1.添加以下依赖项到pom.xml中：

```
<dependency>
  <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
  <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-aop</artifactId>
</dependency>
```

2.在你的Spring Boot应用程序的配置类中添加@EnableAspectJAutoProxy注解启用AOP：

```
@Configuration
@EnableTransactionManagement
@EnableAspectJAutoProxy
public class AppConfig {

}
```

3.创建一个AOP切面类，用于记录所有的成功事务操作SQL：

```
@Aspect
@Component
public class TransactionAspect {

  private static final Logger logger = LoggerFactory.getLogger(TransactionAspect.class);

  @AfterReturning(value = "@annotation(org.springframework.transaction.annotation.Transactional)",returning = "result")
  public void logTransaction(JoinPoint joinPoint, Object result) {
      logger.info("Successful transaction for "+joinPoint.getSignature().getName());
  }
}
```

这个切面会捕捉所有使用@Transactional注解的方法，并记录成功事务操作的SQL。

4.启动应用程序并运行成功的事务操作。在应用程序的日志输出中，你应该看到记录的SQL。

请注意，这种方式将记录所有成功的事务操作SQL，包括那些没有被显式声明为事务操作的SQL。

QueryDSL是一个开源框架，用于以类型安全的方式从Java应用程序中查询数据库。要获取QueryDSL查询的历史SQL，我们可以通过在QueryDSL的Configuration中添加一个Listener来捕获SQL语句。

以下是如何在Spring Boot中使用QueryDSL获取历史SQL：

1.添加以下依赖项到pom.xml中：

```
<dependency>
  <groupId>com.querydsl</groupId>
  <artifactId>querydsl-jpa</artifactId>
  <version>4.4.0</version>
</dependency>
<dependency>
  <groupId>com.querydsl</groupId>
  <artifactId>querydsl-apt</artifactId>
  <version>4.4.0</version>
  <scope>provided</scope>
</dependency>
```

请注意，我们还添加了querydsl-apt依赖项，它用于生成QueryDSL JPA模型类。

2.在Spring Boot应用程序的配置文件中，添加以下配置：

```
spring.jpa.properties.hibernate.ejb.interceptor=com.example.CustomInterceptor
```

这个配置添加了一个自定义拦截器CustomInterceptor，用于捕获QueryDSL查询的历史SQL。

3.创建一个自定义的拦截器CustomInterceptor，并添加以下代码：

```
public class CustomInterceptor extends EmptyInterceptor {

  private static final long serialVersionUID = 1L;

  private ThreadLocal<List<String>> queryCache = new ThreadLocal<>();

  @Override
  public String onPrepareStatement(String sql) {
    if (queryCache.get() != null) {
      queryCache.get().add(sql);
    }
    return super.onPrepareStatement(sql);
  }

  public List<String> getQueryCache() {
    List<String> values = queryCache.get();
    queryCache.remove();
    return values;
  }

  public void clear() {
    queryCache.set(new ArrayList<>());
  }

}
```

这个拦截器会捕获所有的QueryDSL查询SQL，并将它们添加到一个线程本地的列表中，该列表可以在拦截器外部检索。

4.在Spring Boot应用程序中使用QueryDSL来查询数据库。

在要执行的查询之前，使用拦截器的"clear"方法清除历史查询缓存：

```
@Autowired
private JPAQueryFactory queryFactory;

@Autowired
private CustomInterceptor interceptor;

public List<MyEntity> getEntities() {
  interceptor.clear();
  QMyEntity entity = QMyEntity.myEntity;

  return queryFactory.select(entity)
        .from(entity)
        .where(entity.name.eq("John"))
        .fetch();
}
```

在执行查询之后，检索拦截器的查询缓存：

```
List<String> queryCache = interceptor.getQueryCache();
queryCache.forEach(System.out::println); //或者将查询缓存记录到日志中
```

我们可以将历史查询缓存记录到日志文件中，以便后续跟踪和管理。

可以通过Spring Boot的AOP来拦截Hibernate的SQL语句，并记录历史SQL语句。

以下是如何在Spring Boot中使用AOP来获取Hibernate历史SQL：

1.添加以下依赖项到pom.xml中：

```
<dependency> 
  <groupId>org.hibernate</groupId> 
  <artifactId>hibernate-core</artifactId> 
  <version>5.4.32.Final</version> 
</dependency> 
<dependency> 
  <groupId>org.hibernate</groupId> 
  <artifactId>hibernate-entitymanager</artifactId> 
  <version>5.4.32.Final</version> 
</dependency>
```

2.在Spring Boot应用程序的配置文件中，添加以下配置项：

```
spring.jpa.properties.hibernate.show_sql=true //启用Hibernate的SQL日志记录
spring.jpa.properties.hibernate.format_sql=true //格式化Hibernate的SQL输出
logging.level.org.hibernate.SQL=DEBUG //设置Hibernate SQL日志级别为DEBUG
```

3.创建一个Hibernate SQL监听器，并实现"PostInsertEventListener"和"PostUpdateEventListener"接口：

```
@Component
public class HibernateSqlListener implements PostInsertEventListener, PostUpdateEventListener {

  private List<String> sqlList = new ArrayList<>();

  @Override
  public void onPostInsert(PostInsertEvent event) {
    addSql(event.getStatementString());
  }

  @Override
  public void onPostUpdate(PostUpdateEvent event) {
    addSql(event.getStatementString());
  }

  private synchronized void addSql(String sql) {
    sqlList.add(sql);
  }

  public synchronized List<String> getSqlList() {
    List<String> copyList = new ArrayList<>(sqlList);
    sqlList.clear();
    return copyList;
  }

}
```

在这个监听器中，我们维护了一个sqlList列表，用于缓存Hibernate的所有SQL语句。

4.创建一个AOP切面类，并使用以下代码捕获所有的事件：

```
@Aspect
@Component
public class HibernateSqlAspect {

  private static final Logger logger = LoggerFactory.getLogger(HibernateSqlListener.class);

  @Autowired
  private HibernateSqlListener hibernateSqlListener;

  @AfterReturning("execution(* org.hibernate.event.spi.*EventListener+.onPostInsert(..)) ||"
      + " execution(* org.hibernate.event.spi.*EventListener+.onPostUpdate(..))")
  public void logHibernateSql() {
    List<String> sqlList = hibernateSqlListener.getSqlList();
    sqlList.forEach(sql -> logger.debug(sql));
  }

}
```

这个切面会捕获所有的Hibernate PostInsert和PostUpdate事件，并在事件结束后获取Hibernate生成的SQL语句。

5.在Spring Boot应用程序中执行数据库操作，以捕捉和提取SQL语句。在日志输出中，你可以看到所有被捕获的Hibernate SQL语句。

请注意，这种方式记录的实际是Hibernate SQL语句，而不是具体执行的查询语句。

To use Resilience4j with Spring Data JDBC/JPA, you can follow the steps below. In these examples, we will first create a simple Spring Boot application that uses Spring Data JPA, and then we will integrate Resilience4j to implement circuit breaking.

**Example 1: Using Resilience4j with JPA Repositories**

1. Start by creating a Spring Boot application with the following dependencies:

- spring-boot-starter-data-jpa
- spring-boot-starter-web
- resilience4j-spring-boot2 (for Spring Boot 2.x)
- resilience4j-all (optional, if you want to use all features of Resilience4j)

2. Configure your `application.properties` file with database connection settings (for H2 or any other database of your choice).

3. Define an entity and a repository for the entity:

```java
@Entity
public class Person {
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(strategy= GenerationType.AUTO)
    private Long id;
    private String firstName;
    private String lastName;
}

@Repository
public interface PersonRepository extends JpaRepository<Person, Long> {
    List<Person> findByLastName(String lastName);
}
```

4. Create a service class to wrap the repository call and apply Resilience4j circuit breaker functionality:

```java
import io.github.resilience4j.circuitbreaker.CircuitBreaker;
import io.github.resilience4j.circuitbreaker.CircuitBreakerConfig;

@Service
public class PersonService {

    private final PersonRepository personRepository;
    private final CircuitBreaker circuitBreaker;

    public PersonService(PersonRepository personRepository, CircuitBreakerRegistry circuitBreakerRegistry) {
        this.personRepository = personRepository;

        CircuitBreakerConfig circuitBreakerConfig = CircuitBreakerConfig.custom()
                .failureRateThreshold(50)
                .waitDurationInOpenState(Duration.ofMillis(1000))
                .ringBufferSizeInHalfOpenState(2)
                .ringBufferSizeInClosedState(2)
                .build();

        this.circuitBreaker = circuitBreakerRegistry.circuitBreaker("personService", circuitBreakerConfig);
    }

    public List<Person> findPersonsByName(String lastName) {
        return circuitBreaker.executeSupplier(() -> personRepository.findByLastName(lastName));
    }

}
```

5. In your controller, inject the `PersonService` and use it to get the persons by name:

```java
@RestController
public class PersonController {

    private final PersonService personService;

    public PersonController(PersonService personService) {
        this.personService = personService;
    }

    @GetMapping("/persons/{lastName}")
    public List<Person> getPersonsByLastName(@PathVariable String lastName) {
        return personService.findPersonsByName(lastName);
    }
}
```

**Example 2: Using Resilience4j with JdbcTemplate**

1. Assuming you have a Spring Boot project with JPA configured, add the Resilience4j dependencies as described in the first example.

2. To use JdbcTemplate, update your dependencies by adding the `spring-boot-starter-jdbc`.

3. Configure your `application.properties` file with database connection settings as described in the first example.

4. Create a service class to wrap JdbcTemplate calls and apply Resilience4j circuit breaker functionality:

```java
import io.github.resilience4j.circuitbreaker.CircuitBreaker;
import io.github.resilience4j.circuitbreaker.CircuitBreakerConfig;

@Service
public class UserService {

    private final JdbcTemplate jdbcTemplate;
    private final CircuitBreaker circuitBreaker;

    public UserService(JdbcTemplate jdbcTemplate, CircuitBreakerRegistry circuitBreakerRegistry) {
        this.jdbcTemplate = jdbcTemplate;

        CircuitBreakerConfig circuitBreakerConfig = CircuitBreakerConfig.custom()
              .failureRateThreshold(50)
              .waitDurationInOpenState(Duration.ofMillis(1000))
              .ringBufferSizeInHalfOpenState(2)
              .ringBufferSizeInClosedState(2)
              .build();

        this.circuitBreaker = circuitBreakerRegistry.circuitBreaker("userService", circuitBreakerConfig);
    }

    public List<User> findUsersByName(String lastName) {
        return circuitBreaker.executeSupplier(() -> jdbcTemplate.query("SELECT * FROM users WHERE last_name = ?",
            new Object[]{lastName},
            (resultSet, i) -> new User(resultSet.getLong("id"),
                resultSet.getString("first_name"),
                resultSet.getString("last_name"))));
    }
}
```

5. In your controller, inject the `UserService` and use it to get the users by name:

```java
@RestController
public class UserController {

    private final UserService userService;

    public UserController(UserService userService) {
        this.userService = userService;
    }

    @GetMapping("/users/{lastName}")
    public List<User> getUsersByLastName(@PathVariable String lastName) {
        return userService.findUsersByName(lastName);
    }
}
```

Now, when calling the `getPersonsByLastName()` or `getUsersByLastName()` methods, Resilience4j will apply the circuit breaker functionality, limiting the impact of failures when communicating with the database.

可以使用Spring AOP和自定义异常处理器来捕获异常，并将其记录到数据库中。下面是一个简单的实现步骤：

1. 引入Spring AOP和数据库相关依赖：

```xml
<dependency>
    <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
    <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-aop</artifactId>
</dependency>

<dependency>
   <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>
   <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-data-jpa</artifactId>
</dependency>
```

2. 创建自定义异常类，并在异常类中添加需要记录的信息。

```java
public class CustomException extends RuntimeException {
    private String errorCode;
    private String errorMsg;

    public CustomException(String errorCode, String errorMsg) {
        this.errorCode = errorCode;
        this.errorMsg = errorMsg;
    }

    public String getErrorCode() {
        return errorCode;
    }

    public String getErrorMsg() {
        return errorMsg;
    }
}
```

3. 创建异常处理器

在异常处理器中，我们可以使用Spring AOP拦截所有带有`@RestController`注解的控制器方法，当方法抛出`CustomException`异常时，将异常信息记录到数据库中。

```java
@Aspect
@Component
public class ExceptionHandler {
    @Autowired
    private ErrorLogRepository errorLogRepository;

    @Pointcut("execution(public * cn.example.demo.controller.*.*(..))")
    public void webLog() {
    }

    @Around("webLog()")
    public Object doAround(ProceedingJoinPoint joinPoint) throws Throwable {
        Object result = null;
        try {
            result = joinPoint.proceed();
        } catch (CustomException e) {
            //记录异常信息到数据库
            ErrorLog errorLog = new ErrorLog(e.getErrorCode(), e.getErrorMsg());
            errorLogRepository.save(errorLog);
            //抛出异常
            throw e;
        }
        return result;
    }
}
```

4. 创建数据库表和实体类

在我们的例子中，我们创建了一个名为`error_log`的表来存储异常信息。我们为该表创建了一个名为`id`的自增主键，以及`error_code`和`error_msg`字段来存储错误码和错误信息。

```sql
CREATE TABLE error_log (
    id bigint NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
    error_code varchar(50),
    error_msg varchar(1000),
    PRIMARY KEY (id)
);
```

创建实体类`ErrorLog`来映射上面的表：

```java
@Entity
@Table(name = "error_log")
public class ErrorLog {
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)
    private Long id;

    @Column(name = "error_code")
    private String errorCode;

    @Column(name = "error_msg")
    private String errorMsg;

    public ErrorLog() {
    }

    public ErrorLog(String errorCode, String errorMsg) {
        this.errorCode = errorCode;
        this.errorMsg = errorMsg;
    }

    public Long getId() {
        return id;
    }

    public void setId(Long id) {
        this.id = id;
    }

    public String getErrorCode() {
        return errorCode;
    }

    public String getErrorMsg() {
        return errorMsg;
    }

    public void setErrorCode(String errorCode) {
        this.errorCode = errorCode;
    }

    public void setErrorMsg(String errorMsg) {
        this.errorMsg = errorMsg;
    }
}
```

5. 创建一个`ErrorLogRepository`接口，用于对`ErrorLog`实体类操作数据库。

```java
public interface ErrorLogRepository extends JpaRepository<ErrorLog, Long> {
}
```

6. 在控制器方法中抛出自定义异常

当控制器方法抛出`CustomException`异常时，我们的AOP异常处理器将拦截该异常并将错误信息记录到`error_log`表中。

```java
@RestController
public class MyController {
    @Autowired
    private SomeService someService;

    @GetMapping("/test")
    public void test() {
        try {
            someService.doSomething();
        } catch (CustomException e) {
            throw e;
        }
    }
}
```

这样，我们就可以通过AOP和自定义异常处理器将异常信息记录到数据库中了。需要注意的是，异常信息的记录应该根据实际需求来实现，这里仅提供一种简单的实现方式。

Here is an example Java code that demonstrates how log4j can be used to log messages in a Java application:

```java
import org.apache.log4j.Logger;

public class Example {

    private static final Logger logger = Logger.getLogger(Example.class);

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        logger.debug("This is a debug message");
        logger.info("This is an info message");
        logger.warn("This is a warning message");
        logger.error("This is an error message");
        logger.fatal("This is a fatal message");
    }
}
```

This code sets up a logger object using the logger name "Example", and then logs messages at different log levels using the logger.debug, logger.info, logger.warn, logger.error, and logger.fatal methods. By default, these messages will be written to the console, but log4j can be configured to write messages to a file or other destinations as needed.

To dump messages to a file, the log4j.properties file needs to be configured with a file appender. Here's an example log4j.properties file that logs messages to a file called "example.log":

```
log4j.rootLogger=DEBUG, file

log4j.appender.file=org.apache.log4j.RollingFileAppender
log4j.appender.file.File=example.log
log4j.appender.file.MaxFileSize=10MB
log4j.appender.file.MaxBackupIndex=10
log4j.appender.file.layout=org.apache.log4j.PatternLayout
log4j.appender.file.layout.ConversionPattern=%d %p %c{1} - %m%n
```

This configuration sets the root logger's log level to DEBUG and adds a file appender that will write messages to a file called "example.log". The RollingFileAppender is used, which will rotate the log file when it reaches a certain size (in this case, 10 megabytes) and keep up to 10 backups of old log files. The PatternLayout is used to format the log messages, which includes the date, log level, logger name, and message.

With this configuration, any log messages sent to the root logger will be written to the "example.log" file. For example, the following Java code would log messages to the file:

```java
import org.apache.log4j.Logger;

public class Example {

    private static final Logger logger = Logger.getLogger(Example.class);

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        logger.debug("This is a debug message");
        logger.info("This is an info message");
        logger.warn("This is a warning message");
        logger.error("This is an error message");
        logger.fatal("This is a fatal message");
    }
}
```

When this code is executed with the log4j.properties file in the classpath, the log messages will be written to the "example.log" file instead of the console.

Sure, here is a basic code snippet for the bar movement and stopping:

```C#
public class BarController : MonoBehaviour
{
    public float speed = 5f;
    public bool isMoving = false;
    public float targetPositionX = 0f;
    public float barWidth = 100f;
    public float targetMinBounds = -50f;
    public float targetMaxBounds = 50f;

    void Update()
    {
        if (isMoving)
        {
            float posX = transform.position.x + speed * Time.deltaTime;
            transform.position = new Vector2(posX, transform.position.y);

            if (posX >= targetPositionX)
            {
                isMoving = false;
                CheckBarPosition();
            }
        }
    }

    void CheckBarPosition()
    {
        float barPosX = transform.position.x;
        float leftBound = targetPositionX + targetMinBounds;
        float rightBound = targetPositionX + targetMaxBounds;

        if (barPosX >= leftBound && barPosX <= rightBound)
        {
            Debug.Log("Success!");
            // Here you can do something, such as playing a sound, incrementing a score, etc.
        }
        else
        {
            Debug.Log("Missed the area. Try again.");
            // Here you can do something, such as playing a sound or asking the player to retry the game.
        }
    }

    public void StartMoving()
    {
        isMoving = true;
        targetPositionX = Random.Range(-barWidth / 2f, barWidth / 2f);
    }

    public void StopMoving()
    {
        isMoving = false;
        CheckBarPosition();
    }
}
```

This script assumes you have already created the UI elements for the game, such as the bar image and any buttons or input controls you want to use. Here's how the script works:

- The `speed` variable determines how fast the bar moves across the screen. You can adjust this to make the game more or less challenging.
- `isMoving` is a boolean that tracks whether the bar is currently moving or not.
- `targetPositionX` is the target position for the bar image to stop within the designated area.
- `barWidth` is used to calculate the bounds for the designated area of the bar image.
- `targetMinBounds` and `targetMaxBounds` set the range of acceptable positions for the bar image to stop within.
- In the `Update` function, if the `isMoving` variable is true, the bar moves across the screen from left to right until it reaches the `targetPositionX` value, at which point it stops moving and calls the `CheckBarPosition` function.
- The `CheckBarPosition` function calculates the position of the bar image and compares it to the designated area's boundaries. If the bar's position is within the acceptable range, the game is declared successful. Otherwise, the game is missed, and the player must try again. You can customize this logic to suit your game's needs.
- The `StartMoving` function is called to start moving the bar once the player taps the screen or triggers another input control. It sets `isMoving` to true and generates a random target position within the `barWidth` range.
- The `StopMoving` function is called to stop the bar's movement once the player taps the screen again. It sets `isMoving` to false and calls the `CheckBarPosition` function to check if the bar's position is within the acceptable range.

This is just a basic skeleton script, and you can customize it to match your specific game needs, such as adding sound effects, different levels of difficulty, and increasing speed based on the player's performance.

你可以使用以下代码来实现：

```csharp
DateTime now = DateTime.Now;
DateTime targetTime;

while (true)
{
    bool anyDateTimePickerAfterNow = false;
    for (int i = 0; i < 10; i++)
    {
        targetTime = dateTimePickerArray[i].Value;
        if (targetTime > now)
        {
            anyDateTimePickerAfterNow = true;
            break;
        }
    }

    if (anyDateTimePickerAfterNow)
    {
        break; // 跳出循环
    }
    else
    {
        // 继续等待
        Thread.Sleep(1000);
    }
}
```

其中 `dateTimePickerArray` 是包含了所有 `DateTimePicker` 控件的数组。代码中先声明当前时间 `now`，然后循环比较每个控件的时间。如果有任何一个控件的时间大于当前时间，就设置标志位 `anyDateTimePickerAfterNow` 为 `true` 并跳出循环。否则就等待一秒钟再继续比较，直到有控件的时间大于当前时间。

